ing</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">23</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"BlackBin\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Fri</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">25</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Black Bin</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">30</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"MonthLabel\"><h4>August 2025</h4></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">06</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"BlackBin\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Fri</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">08</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Black Bin</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">13</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">20</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"BlackBin\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Fri</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">22</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Black Bin</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Thu</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">28</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"MonthLabel\"><h4>September 2025</h4></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">03</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"BlackBin\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Fri</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">05</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Black Bin</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">10</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">17</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li><li class=\"BlackBin\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Fri</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">19</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Black Bin</span></li><li class=\"Recycling\"><span class=\"wasteName\">Wed</span> <span class=\"wasteDay\">24</span> <span class=\"wasteType\">Recycling</span></li></ul><br></br><br></br><br></br><h2>Service Messages </h2><h4><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Presenting Bins by 6am</span></h4><p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Residents will need to put their bins and bags out by 6am on the morning or evening before their collection from now on. The new, earlier display time, of 6am rather than 7am, is to enable the crews to have more flexible working hours if and when needed. We thank you in advance for your understanding and cooperation</span></strong></span></p><h4><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\">Green Bin Collection</span></h4><p><span style=\"font-family: verdana, geneva, sans-serif;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\">Green bin collection dates will only be displayed while there is a valid in-date permit at the property. If the permit has expired, no future collection dates will be displayed until a new permit is purchased.<br>To purchase or renew a green bin subscription visit our website</span></strong> <span style=\"font-size: 12pt;\"><strong><a href=\"https://my.northdevon.gov.uk/service/Green_bin_service\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener\">Garden waste service</a></strong></span></span></p>","type":"text","data-type":"text","name":"Results2","id":"Results2","data-name":"Results2","aria-labelledby":"label_Results2 Results2 prefix_Results2 helpText_Results2","readonly":"true","required":"true","class":"col-xs-11 col-sm-11     fs-hidden-field required alignAbove fieldInput text read_only_field ","data-hidden":"true","data-output-format":"normal","data-mandatory-message":"This field is required","data-min-message":"Please input at least _min_value_ characters","data-max-message":"Pleas